        <item>
            <title>Version 2.0.4</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li>Fixed app hanging indefinitely when opening audio files (especially with embedded album art) from Finder</li>
                    <li>Improved overall responsiveness during file load and music-mode transitions</li>
                    <li>Smoother fullscreen transitions — no more black frame on exit</li>
                    <li>Larger Play/Pause button hit area in the controls bar</li>
                </ul>
